scenes.description: Opening title screen for Blue Journey 1st Live "Yoake no Uta."
A slideshow featuring a collection of handwritten messages from fans and illustrations of the performing members.
Promotion of various concert merchandise, including penlights, t-shirts, towels, bags, and acrylic stands.
An informative slide explaining the concert's narrative format and reminding attendees to prepare for the 'journey'.
